title: I recreated the Rings of Power with a vibrating square

media:group.media:title: I recreated the Rings of Power with a vibrating square
media:group.media:description:
If you or someone you know would like a paid internship in New York, London, Hong Kong or Singapore check out Jane Street: https://bit.ly/janestreet-stevemould

The title sequence from Lord of The Rings: The Rings Of Power looks a lot like Chladni figures (2D standing waves) so I tried to recreate it!

You can buy my books here:
